metatags.og:description: French Lick, Indiana -- located in the southern portion of the state -- is home to the Big Splash Adventure Indoor Water Park & Resort and Patoka Lake. The latter provides 8,800 acres of water, as well as fishing and boating opportunities. French Lick is the locale of the Indiana Railway Museum; the museum offers a 10 mile train ride that passes through the town of Cuzco. (See Reference 5)
